Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,CAT-ROUTER. Five LLM tasks, five different best models. Kamiwaza picks\Nthem automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A Marine analyst submits a daily intel brief workflow. Vision,\Nclassification, long-context synthesis, tool calling, hero narrative.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight models in the on-prem catalog. Vision, tool calling, security\Nposture, hardware home — all metadata-tagged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Per-task routing decisions. Qwen-VL for vision, Llama 8B for fast\Nclassify, Qwen 72B for long context, Llama 3.3 70B for tool calls, …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Toggle Fast slash Cheap mode. The catalog reroutes everything to Llama\Nthree point one eight B. Cost drops eighty percent. Quality drops …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator sees the trade-off live: per-task cost, latency, and quality\Nside by side. Hash-chained audit of every routing decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One environment variable swaps the synthetic catalog for a live\NKamiwaza Model Gateway behind the SCIF.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,CAT-ROUTER. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Right model, right task,\Nright pod — every time.
